\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Reconfigurability
\f0\b0 : P4 allows modifying packet processing logic after deployment, unlike traditional networking hardware with fixed behavior.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
